{"tid":1515374,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去台中又要買「手信」","createTime":"2019-08-29T06:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T08:28:29.000Z","uid":158325,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4221b03f2473f87f3db3f4f899d1c8aeb50b1f","tid":1515374,"uid":158325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"嚟緊或者會去台中買裝備既巴/絲打<br />\n我推介一間係逢甲夜市附近既良心五金行<br />\n佢地都有留意香港發生緊既事<br />\n一聽到我喺香港嚟問口罩啲嘢就話冇貨<br />\n好多香港人嚟買<br />\n但佢可以即刻訂到翻嚟<br />\n例如我今日訂既<br />\n佢就第2朝8、9點就會有貨翻到嚟<br />\n又會計平比我<br />\n我買3M6200 920台紙+2個濾罐<br />\n走前又同我講香港加油、小心啲<br />\n好窩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎翻嚟就塞背囊過關上機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命<br />\n光復香港<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rg4sAuu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frg4sAuu.png&h=0fb15b51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"465da2e674c0a50571d8846c3e846895235280a6","tid":1515374,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"d4d5520ee68bad6af4608206e3ec8d68d8e4bbcd","tid":1515374,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:40:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求入黎幫推</span></span><br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士進程請入，一個也不能少不是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00d0601dacc4b82bf7846a7f82ba258aa3e52b47","tid":1515374,"uid":158325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-